cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as relation classification. It may also belong to "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as it proposes a neural network-based approach for the task. Additionally, it could be categorized under "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves developing a model to understand the semantic representation of text. "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible sub-category as the paper proposes a neural network-based approach. Finally, "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) could also be a relevant sub-category as relation classification is a task that is often used in information retrieval systems.
